            "title": "【中環解密】擔保成報傳媒貸款  楊家誠被判須還2.34億",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"【中環解密】擔保成報傳媒貸款 楊家誠被判須還2.34億\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"504\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5vdByfzevuRGDdyHAd9qAg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwNA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/66195c10-2970-11f1-b7ff-fc7ecbcbd7d4\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">【中環解密】擔保成報傳媒貸款 楊家誠被判須還2.34億</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
